    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "you said wind is a \"clean energy source\" though... isnt there a lot of environmental damage from mining all the materials needed for the turbines and the batteries for storage? feels like it might not be as \"clean\" as people say.",
      "source": "evaluator"
